HEADWORD: Quietist
<hw>Qui"et*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>qui⟦eacute⟧tiste</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld> <def>One of
